text:
He told her she was the greatest joy in his whole life,
And if she’d agree, he’d make her his one and only wife;
She couldn’t bring herself to turn him down, so off to the church they went,
Young Will was the last thing on her mind, and young Sue was fully content;
Afterward he kissed her and settled her right onto his knee,
There wasn’t a single man on earth half as loving as he!
